    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Fair-condition car that appears to be a decent driver but clearly shows age and use. Expect noticeable cosmetic wear, some imperfections inside and out, and an overall presentation that is respectable but not especially sharp or fresh. It should suit someone looking for an affordable, usable car and not a fully sorted or show-quality example, and a buyer should come expecting the possibility of minor repairs, maintenance items, or deferred needs.",
