    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for someone seeking inexpensive transportation or a solid project opportunity. It shows its age and is being advertised accordingly, but it still offers real value for the right buyer who appreciates a straightforward deal. If you want an affordable entry point without paying retail for a cleaner example, this one deserves a look.",
