      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left in it? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a great budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transport or a handy little project. It starts, runs, and offers real value for the money, with the kind of honest character you\u2019d expect from a well-used vehicle. If you want something inexpensive that can get the job done without breaking the bank, this one is well worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Great budget-friendly project with strong platform potential. The engine fires up and the drivetrain feels fundamentally intact, making this a solid candidate for someone looking for an affordable driver, restoration base, or weekend wrenching project. Shows cosmetic wear and needs attention consistent with age and use, but the core mechanical package is there. If you know these cars, you know the value in a complete, honest example with plenty of upside. Priced to move for the right enthusiast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 8
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
