      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle offers an accessible way into dependable transportation at a great value. Best suited for a practical buyer, first-time driver, or someone looking for a solid project, it presents an opportunity to own a vehicle at a very attractive price point. Priced to sell and represented honestly, this is a smart chance to secure affordable wheels without overspending.",
